    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An earth pigment containing red iron oxide, originally obtained from Spain. It is a coarse grain, an inexpensive colorant, having a dull red color, and used in industrial paints.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
